[[Leeds United F.C.|Leeds United]], and Spanish goalkeeper [[Ricardo L\u00f3pez Felipe|Ricardo]], who signed for just \u00a31.5&nbsp;million.\n\nOn 5 June, [[Lee Roche]] was released from United on a free transfer. On 30 June, defender [[Laurent Blanc]] announced his retirement from football. Also on 30 June, [[David May (footballer)|David May]] was released.\n\n===In===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Pos.\n! Name\n! From\n! Fee\n|-\n| 22 July 2002\n| DF\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Rio Ferdinand]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Leeds United A.F.C.|Leeds United]]\n| \u00a329.1m\n|-\n| 30 August 2002\n| GK\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ricardo L\u00f3pez Felipe|Ricardo]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Valladolid]]\n| \u00a31.5m\n|}\n\n===Out===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Pos.\n! Name\n! To\n! Fee\n|-\n| 7 July 2002\n| GK\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Nick Culkin]]\n|colspan=\"2\"| Released\n|-\n| 26 July 2002\n| FW\n| {{flagicon|TRI}} [[Dwight Yorke]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Blackburn Rovers F.C.|Blackburn Rovers]]\n| \u00a32m\n|-\n| 5 June 2003\n| DF\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} John Cogger\n|colspan=\"2\"| Released<ref name=\"rochereleased\">{{cite news|url=http://www.manutd.com/news/fullstory.sps?inewsid=36727 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051217111639/http://www.manutd.com/news/fullstory.sps?inewsid=36727 |archivedate=17 December 2005 |title=Roche released |work=ManUtd.com |publisher=Manchester United Football Club |first=Simon |last=Davies |date=3 June 2003 |accessdate=21 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 5 June 2003\n| DF\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Lee Roche]]\n|colspan=\"2\"| Released<ref name=\"rochereleased\"/>\n|-\n| 5 June 2003\n| DF\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[David May (footballer)|David May]]\n|colspan=\"2\"| Released<ref name=\"rochereleased\"/>\n|-\n| 5 June 2003\n| FW\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Kalam Mooniaruck]]\n|colspan=\"2\"| Released<ref name=\"rochereleased\"/>\n|-\n| 5 June 2003\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[John Rankin (footballer)|John Rankin]]\n|colspan=\"2\"| Rel